/Helvetica findfont 12 scalefont setfont
72 740 moveto /Helvetica-Bold findfont 24 scalefont setfont (Power Map Canvas) show
/Helvetica findfont 12 scalefont setfont
72 715 moveto (Use this canvas to map who is impacted vs who has influence.) show
/Helvetica findfont 10 scalefont setfont
72 695 moveto (1. Write the demand and win statement at the top.) show
72 680 moveto (2. Place the PRIMARY TARGET in the center circle.) show
72 665 moveto (3. Add secondary targets in the middle ring.) show
72 650 moveto (4. Add allies/opponents/undecided in the outer ring.) show
72 635 moveto (5. Draw arrows for relationships and record follow-ups below.) show

% Demand box
newpath 72 600 moveto 468 0 rlineto 0 -35 rlineto -468 0 rlineto closepath stroke
/Helvetica-Bold findfont 11 scalefont setfont
78 612 moveto (Demand:) show
newpath 72 550 moveto 468 0 rlineto 0 -35 rlineto -468 0 rlineto closepath stroke
78 562 moveto (Win Statement:) show

% Circles
/Helvetica findfont 11 scalefont setfont
newpath 306 360 180 0 360 arc stroke
newpath 306 360 140 0 360 arc stroke
newpath 306 360 95 0 360 arc stroke
296 365 moveto (PRIMARY) show
292 350 moveto (TARGET) show
266 510 moveto (Secondary) show
266 225 moveto (Secondary) show
220 545 moveto (Allies / Opponents / Moveable) show

% Legend
/Helvetica-Bold findfont 12 scalefont setfont
80 240 moveto (Legend) show
/Helvetica findfont 10 scalefont setfont
0 0.6 0 setrgbcolor
newpath 80 220 moveto 20 0 rlineto 0 12 rlineto -20 0 rlineto closepath fill
0 setgray
110 224 moveto (Ally) show
1 0.8 0 setrgbcolor
newpath 80 200 moveto 20 0 rlineto 0 12 rlineto -20 0 rlineto closepath fill
0 setgray
110 204 moveto (Moveable) show
1 0.2 0 setrgbcolor
newpath 80 180 moveto 20 0 rlineto 0 12 rlineto -20 0 rlineto closepath fill
0 setgray
110 184 moveto (Opponent) show

% Follow-up Tracker
/Helvetica-Bold findfont 13 scalefont setfont
72 160 moveto (Follow-up Tracker) show
/Helvetica-Bold findfont 10 scalefont setfont
/cols [150 100 90 150 80] def
/labels [(Influence Node)(Category)(Owner)(Next Action)(Due Date)] def
0 1 4 {
  /i exch def
  /w cols i get def
  /x 72 def
  0 1 i 1 sub { /j exch def /x x cols j get add def } for
  newpath x 140 moveto w 0 rlineto 0 -25 rlineto w neg 0 rlineto closepath stroke
  x 145 moveto labels i get show
  0 1 3 {
    /row exch def
    newpath x 140 25 row add -25 mul add moveto w 0 rlineto 0 -25 rlineto w neg 0 rlineto closepath stroke
  } for
} for
showpage
